comments: Beverley (LAC) steps into Bogdanovic (IND) and delivers contact that affects Bogdanovic's ability to land.
Matthews (IND) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Williams (LAC).
Sabonis (IND) establishes himself in a legal picking position in Gilgeous-Alexander's (LAC) path and absorbs the contact.
Gilgeous-Alexander (LAC) makes contact to Sabonis' (IND) arm during his shooting motion that affects his play at the basket.
Matthews (IND) makes marginal contact with Gallinari (LAC) at the start of the drive and Gallinari is able to play through the contact.
Young (IND) maintains a legal guarding position on Williams (LAC) during the drive.
Sabonis (IND) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Williams (LAC).
Gallinari (LAC) jumps alongside Evans (IND) and does not deliver contact as he legally contests the shot attempt.
Beverley (LAC) establishes himself in a legal picking position in the path of Matthews (IND).
Bogdanovic (IND) maintains a legal guarding position during the jump shot attempt by Williams (LAC).
Sabonis (IND) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Thornwell (LAC) and does not deliver contact.
Gallinari (LAC) makes marginal contact with Evans (IND) after his gather, but he is able to move through the contact during his driving shot attempt.
Beverley (LAC) establishes himself in a legal picking position in the path of Matthews (IND) and does not deliver contact.
Beverley (LAC) maintains a legal pivot foot.
Evans (IND) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Beverley (LAC).
Beverley (LAC) moves legally alongside of Bogdanovic (IND) during the drive as Bogdanovic slips and falls on his own.
Bogdanovic (IND) extends his leg and kicks the ball.
Bogdanovic (IND) and Thornwell (LAC) make incidental contact with each other as they are both attempting to retrieve the loose ball.
Young (IND) commits a take foul on Gilgeous-Alexander (LAC).
